#Handle events for VALEMPESS_CSTD
#**
#* Label for coding event of CRUD
#* @param CURPTH Local Char(250), contains the class path
#* @param AEVENT Local Char(20), contains the event code
#* @return ASTATUS Local Integer
#*!
$EVENTS
Case [L]CURPTH
   When ""
    Case [L]AEVENT
      When "AREAD_AFTER" : Gosub AREAD_AFTER
      When Default       : Return
    Endcase
Endcase
Return
############################################################################################################
$AREAD_AFTER
Local File FACILITY [FCY]
Local Char VEXT(3) : VEXT = "pdf"
Local Char FILT(250)

Read [FCY]FCY0 = this.FCY
If !fstat
  this.TCH_CPY = [FCY]LEGCPY
Endif

#Add IDENT1 Value
#FRLAA X3-70855 2018-03-01 - START
this.IDENT1 = this.BUL+"."+VEXT
#this.IDENT1 = this.EMP+"~"+this.CTRNUM+"~"+this.BUL+"."+VEXT
#FRLAA X3-70855 2018-03-01 - END

LogicClose File [FCY]
Return





